To test whether a host is alive or not

Command : ping -C 5 dishtv.in


Working Flow (Step-by-Step):
1.Your system sends an ICMP Echo Request to the target.
2.Target receives the request and sends an ICMP Echo Reply.


Default TTL Values : It Helps To Target System  OS
OS	Default TTL
Linux	64
macOS	64
Windows	128
Cisco / Network Devices	255
